These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-1::.
There are 2 different nationalities: malaysian, american
The people use 2 different means of transport: motorbike, taxi
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: march, january
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: action, sports
1. the person watching action movies is not to the right of the person driving the taxi##8
2. the person driving the taxi is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in march##5
3. the malaysian is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |
| Nationality      | american     | malaysian      |
| Transport          | taxi | motorbike    |
| Birthday         | january   | march |
| Movie-Genre   | action  | sports      |

