.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, iced-tea
2 different pets are kept: mouse, horse
House: wooden, palace
City: miami, nizza
1. the person drinking iced-tea is on the far right##1
2. the owner of the mouse is somewhere to the left of the wooden house##5
3. the palace house is not to the right of the wooden house##8
4. the person traveling to miami is not the owner of the horse##6

.:: Answer ::.
|             |         1          |      2      |
| Beverage    | almond-milk        | iced-tea    |
| Pet       | mouse         | horse |
| House         | palace | wooden   |
| City   | miami               | nizza  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-3::.
2 different games are played: poker, chess
City: rome, marseilles
There are 2 different favourite beverages: sprite, cola
2 different pets are kept: cat, ferret
1. the person drinking sprite is in an odd position##4
2. the person drinking cola is not to the right of the owner of the ferret##8
3. the person traveling to rome is somewhere to the left of the person playing chess##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |
| Game   | poker       | chess |
| City   | rome       | marseilles    |
| Beverage   | sprite | cola |
| Pet           | cat        | ferret   |

