2. the person playing billiard is not to the left of the person driving the tram##8
3. the person driving the tram is on the left of the person playing billiard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |
| Game         | bridge | billiard  |
| Color           | amber  | light-blue |
| Birthday   | june | october   |
| Transport     | tram   | airplane |

