The people have 2 different jobs:  coach, doctor
1. the doctor is on the far left##1
2. the person playing whist is not to the right of the fan of ambient##8
3. the fan of ambient is on the right of the fan of funk##1
4. the person playing whist is on the left of the person watching scientific movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |
| Movie-Genre   | documentary | scientific |
| Music-Genre   | funk    | ambient     |
| Game         | whist  | scrabble    |
| Job     | doctor     | coach       |

