There are 2 different favourite colors: ebony, black
1. the person who likes black is on the left of the person who likes ebony##1
2. the person playing mah-jongg is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1
3. the person who likes ebony is not the person watching drama movies##6
4. the person watching drama movies is not to the right of the person who likes ebony##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |
